# Testimonials live here as one Markdown file each, e.g. `jane-smith.md`:
#
#     ---
#     quote: 'She transformed a patch of nettles into somewhere we actually sit.'
#     author: 'Jane Smith'
#     location: 'Bramley'      # optional
#     date: 2026-05-01
#     ---
#
# The Testimonials section renders nothing at all while this directory has no
# entries — an empty "What clients say" heading reads as a gap, so the whole
# block is omitted rather than shown empty. Adding the first file makes it
# appear with no code change.
#
# This file only exists to keep the directory in git. Delete it once there are
# real testimonials, or leave it — the glob only picks up *.md.
